WEBVTT

00:00:05.364 --> 00:00:12.065
In the 1980s, in communist
Eastern Germany,

00:00:12.089 --> 00:00:15.263
if you owned a typewriter,

00:00:15.287 --> 00:00:18.088
you had to register it
with the government.

00:00:18.112 --> 00:00:23.576
You had to register a sample sheet of text
out of the typewriter.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.151
And this was done
so the government could track

00:00:27.175 --> 00:00:28.920
where the text was coming from.

00:00:28.944 --> 00:00:34.639
If they found a paper
which had the wrong kind of thought,